Dialogue: 0,00:00:03.10,00:00:07.07,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ミナト)８本目の尾まで\N封印が解放してしまうと➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked it into the seal spell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.23,0:00:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,so that I would appear within\Nyour psyche,
Dialogue: 0,00:00:07.07,00:00:10.10,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺が\Nお前の意識の中に出てくるよう➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,should the seal be broken to the point\Nyou sprouted the eighth tail.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:10.10,00:00:13.12,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,封印式に細工しておいたのさ。
Dialogue: 0,00:00:13.12,00:00:16.81,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なるべく\Nそうなってほしくはなかったが。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.07,0:00:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I really wanted to avoid that...
Dialogue: 0,00:00:16.81,00:00:22.03,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もうお前に\N会いたくなかったしね 九尾。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I had no desire to see\Nyou again... Nine-Tails.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:24.88,00:00:26.97,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,でも…。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then again...
Dialogue: 0,00:00:29.02,00:00:34.97,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,成長した息子に会えるのは\N少し楽しみでもあったから➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.75,0:00:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I did look forward to seeing\Nmy son as a young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.63,0:00:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll call it even.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:34.97,00:00:37.03,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,イーブンってとこかな。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Fourth Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,00:00:37.03,00:00:44.19,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,四代目火影！\N来い！ ズタズタにしてやる！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.35,0:00:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here!\NI'll rip you to shreds!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if that's the case,\NI'll stay away.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:44.19,00:00:47.99,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ズタズタにするって言ってんのに\N近づかないよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,00:00:47.99,00:00:50.84,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もっともだろ？ ナルト。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto... My name...
Dialogue: 0,00:00:50.84,00:00:53.97,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ナルト)ナルトって 俺の名前。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:01:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How come the Fourth Hokage\Nknows my name?
Dialogue: 0,00:00:57.55,00:01:02.53,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,どうして\N四代目火影が俺の名前を？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.04,0:01:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I'm the one who named you.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:02.53,00:01:07.29,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ん？ だってお前の名前は\N俺がつけたんだから。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}are{\i0} my son, after all.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:07.29,00:01:13.70,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,せがれなんだし。\Nせがれ… じゃあ 俺ってば…。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Son? Then... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard me.\NYou're my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Fourth!
Dialogue: 0,00:01:32.52,00:01:38.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うん さっきも言ったろ\N俺の息子だよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Loud fellow, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go somewhere quiet.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:45.67,00:01:50.51,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ハ… ハハハハッ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The Third didn't tell you much\Nof anything, did he?
Dialogue: 0,00:01:50.51,00:01:55.56,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,グォ～ッ 四代目！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he wanted to suppress as much\Ninformation about Nine-Tails as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If people had found out\Nyou were my son,
Dialogue: 0,00:01:55.56,00:01:58.03,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うるさいね 後ろの。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.92,0:01:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd have been in danger.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:58.03,00:02:01.15,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,少し別のところに行くよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,00:02:06.65,00:02:09.40,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ヘヘッ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you seal the Nine-Tails\Ninside your own son?!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:09.40,00:02:12.50,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,三代目は\N何も言わなかったようだね。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what I went\Nthrough because of that?!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:12.50,00:02:14.59,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,九尾にかかわる情報を➡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All the grown-ups looked\Nat me with contempt...
Dialogue: 0,00:02:14.59,00:02:17.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なるべく\N伏せておきたかったんだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.20,0:02:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And I couldn't make any friends.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:17.47,00:02:22.31,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,息子とわかれば いろいろと\N危険が降りかかるからね。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted people to accept me,
Dialogue: 0,00:02:22.31,00:02:25.33,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,父ちゃん…。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,so I trained really hard\Nto become strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I met Iruka-sensei, and Kakashi-sensei,\Nand Pervy Sage...
Dialogue: 0,00:02:27.81,00:02:29.82,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うぅ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was happy because\Nthey helped make me stronger!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:29.82,00:02:33.72,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なんで息子の俺に九尾なんか\N封印したんだってばよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But because of that, a group called\Nthe Akatsuki came after me,
Dialogue: 0,00:02:33.72,00:02:36.85,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,おかげで俺ってば\Nすっげえ大変だったんだぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,so I had to train even more.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:36.85,00:02:40.54,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,大人たちはみんな 俺のことを\N冷たい目で見やがるし。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I got to be even stronger,\Nbut the Akatsuki still killed my friends.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:40.54,00:02:44.96,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,友達も なかなかできねえし。\Nだから俺 頑張って 頑張って➡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But... huh?\NWhat am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,00:02:44.96,00:02:48.86,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,みんなに認めてもらいたくって\Nすっげえ修業して強くなって➡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, am I supposed\Nto be happy or mad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anymore!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:48.86,00:02:52.82,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そしたらイルカ先生やカカシ先生\Nエロ仙人と出会えて➡
Dialogue: 0,00:02:52.82,00:02:55.71,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,強くなることができて\N嬉しかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto... How old are you now?
Dialogue: 0,00:02:55.71,00:02:59.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,でもそのせいで 暁なんてやつらに\N狙われることになっちまって➡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sixteen.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:59.47,00:03:02.49,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だからもっと修業しなくちゃ\Nなんなくなっちまって。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... You're already\Nsixteen years old, huh?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:02.49,00:03:05.28,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,せっかく\N強くなれることができたのに➡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been hard for you...
Dialogue: 0,00:03:05.28,00:03:07.30,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,仲間が暁にやられて…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:07.30,00:03:09.97,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,でも あれ？ 俺 何…。
Dialogue: 0,00:03:09.97,00:03:12.58,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あ～っ 嬉しいんだか\N腹が立つんだか➡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose after putting\Nmy own son through so much...
Dialogue: 0,00:03:12.58,00:03:14.60,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もうわかんねえってばよ！
Dialogue: 0,00:03:14.60,00:03:18.39,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no right to act like\Na father and apologize.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:18.39,00:03:21.94,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ナルト 何歳になる？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right... already.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:21.94,00:03:25.80,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うっ… 16歳。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the son... of the Fourth Hokage...\Nso I can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:25.80,00:03:31.72,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そうか もう16か。\Nいろいろ大変だったんだよな。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I sealed half of the Nine-Tails' chakra\Ninside of you,
Dialogue: 0,00:03:31.72,00:03:35.37,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ナルト すまなかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,because I believed\Nyou could control its power.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:35.37,00:03:39.41,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,息子のお前につらい思いばかり\Nさせてしまった俺が➡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you are my son.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:39.41,00:03:43.27,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,父親ヅラして謝るのも違うかな。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And there is a reason why I did this.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:45.60,00:03:52.18,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いいよ もう…。\N四代目の火影の息子なんだから➡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When the Nine-Tails attacked\Nthe village sixteen years ago,
Dialogue: 0,00:03:52.18,00:03:56.59,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,我慢する…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:56.59,00:03:59.73,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前に九尾のチャクラを半分残して\N封印したのは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a mastermind\Nwho manipulated the Nine-Tails
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to attack the village.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:59.73,00:04:04.74,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,この力を使いこなすと\N信じていたからだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mastermind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A powerful ninja at that.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:04.74,00:04:10.82,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺の息子ならと…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It would require a special kind of power\Nto go up against such an opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe he will attack our village again.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:10.82,00:04:16.91,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なぜ わざわざそんなことを\Nしたのかには理由がある。
Dialogue: 0,00:04:16.91,00:04:20.53,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,今から16年前\N九尾が里を襲ったとき➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Leaf Village\Nhas already been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:20.53,00:04:24.53,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,わかったことがある。\N何？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... I watched from inside you.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:24.53,00:04:28.57,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あのとき 九尾を操り\N里を襲わせた黒幕がいる。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You watched?!
Dialogue: 0,00:04:28.57,00:04:32.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,黒幕？\Nそれも かなりの力を持つ忍だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I know about Jiraiya-sensei too.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:32.47,00:04:36.43,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,特別な力がなければ\Nとうてい 太刀打ちできない。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then was it Pain who used the Nine-Tails\Nto attack the village before?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:36.43,00:04:40.71,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,おそらく そいつは また里を襲う。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No... It wasn't him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Then who was it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:45.16,00:04:50.31,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もう 木ノ葉の里は\N潰されちまったってばよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The one with the mask.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:50.31,00:04:55.25,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あぁ 見てた。 お前の中からね。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then...\Nhe read through every action I took.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:55.25,00:04:58.04,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,えっ… 見てたって…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He's no ordinary ninja.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:58.04,00:05:00.85,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,自来也先生のことも知ってるよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This man is probably just using Pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Pain had a grudge\Nagainst the Hidden Leaf!
Dialogue: 0,00:05:03.60,00:05:08.30,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それじゃ 前に九尾を使って\N里を襲ったのは ペインなのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, long ago, his own village\Nwas wiped out like ours!
Dialogue: 0,00:05:08.30,00:05:12.82,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いや違う そいつじゃない。\N誰だってばよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that hatred,\Nhe's being used.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:12.82,00:05:17.31,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,暁の１人 面をしている男だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Used?! Someone strong like him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about\Nthis mastermind masked ninja?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is everyone attacking the Leaf?
Dialogue: 0,00:05:21.70,00:05:26.22,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あのとき やつは俺の動きを\Nすべて見切った。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps as long as there is\Na ninja system in this world,
Dialogue: 0,00:05:26.22,00:05:29.25,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ただ者じゃないよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,there can be no peace.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:29.25,00:05:33.28,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,おそらくペインは\Nそいつに利用されているだけだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Pain questioned you about peace...
Dialogue: 0,00:05:33.28,00:05:37.11,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,違う！\Nペインは木ノ葉に恨みを持ってた。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But finding the answer is difficult.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:37.11,00:05:40.69,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,昔 同じように\N自分たちの里もやられたって。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How would you confront this hatred,\Nin order to create peace?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:05:40.69,00:05:45.15,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そのとおりだ。\Nだから そこを利用された。
Dialogue: 0,00:05:45.15,00:05:48.94,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,利用されたって!?\Nあんな強えやつが？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to save something dear...\Nwars are waged.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:48.94,00:05:52.87,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それに\N黒幕だっていう面の忍まで。
Dialogue: 0,00:05:52.87,00:05:55.90,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なんで こんなに\N木ノ葉ばかりが狙われるんだ！
Dialogue: 0,00:05:55.90,00:05:59.72,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,この世に忍のシステムがある限り➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:06:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as there is love,\Nthere will be hate.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:59.72,00:06:03.20,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,平和な秩序は\Nないのかもしれない。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And some will take advantage\Nof that hatred.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:03.20,00:06:06.37,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ペインは\Nお前に平和について問うたが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This monster known as hate will\Nnot die while there is a system of ninja.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:06.37,00:06:09.99,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,答えを見つけるのは難しい。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It will give birth to more Pains.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:09.99,00:06:15.93,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((お前なら 平和を作るため\Nこの憎しみと どう向き合う？))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Pain who killed Jiraiya-sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but upon careful thought,\Nit can be said
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that the chaotic world of the ninja,\Nwhich gave rise to Pain, is equally guilty.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:21.05,00:06:26.58,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,大切なものを救おうとすることで\N戦いが生まれ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,To be a ninja is to confront hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Each and every one of us battles hatred.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:29.99,00:06:34.52,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,愛が存在し続ける限り\N同時に憎しみが生まれ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiraiya-sensei trusted you to find\Na way to end this hatred.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:34.52,00:06:37.44,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,憎しみに忍が利用される。
Dialogue: 0,00:06:37.44,00:06:40.36,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,この忍のシステムがある限り➡
Dialogue: 0,00:06:40.36,00:06:45.40,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,憎しみというバケモノは\Nまた新たなペインを生み出していく。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I can't forgive Pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:45.40,00:06:49.23,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,自来也先生を殺したのは\Nペインだが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,00:06:49.23,00:06:51.67,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,よくよく考えれば➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Fourth... Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,00:06:51.67,00:06:55.67,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そのペインを生み出した\Nこの忍の世の無秩序が➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,00:06:55.67,00:06:58.69,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,先生を殺したも同然なのさ。
Dialogue: 0,00:06:58.69,00:07:02.73,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,忍とは\Nその憎しみとの戦いなんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You must find the answer yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not have the answer.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:02.73,00:07:07.50,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,どの忍も\Nその憎しみと戦っている。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If Pervy Sage and you don't know\Nthe answer, how am I to know?!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:07.50,00:07:12.37,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,自来也先生は\Nこの憎しみを終わらせる答えを➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone expects too much!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:12.37,00:07:14.80,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前に託したんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not smart!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:14.80,00:07:18.84,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だからって俺は ペインを許せねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not a great ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,00:07:18.84,00:07:21.97,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,許すことなんてできねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you'll find the answer.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:21.97,00:07:24.20,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あぁ。
Dialogue: 0,00:07:24.20,00:07:28.02,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,四代目 教えてくれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I have faith in you.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:28.02,00:07:31.26,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺ってば どうしたらいい？
Dialogue: 0,00:07:34.98,00:07:37.59,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,答えは自分で探すんだ。
Dialogue: 0,00:07:37.59,00:07:41.25,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,その答えは 俺にもわからないよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You really believe I can do it?
Dialogue: 0,00:07:41.25,00:07:44.27,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,エロ仙人や四代目すら\Nわかんなかったことが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,To be a parent is to have\Nundying faith in one's child.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:44.27,00:07:46.29,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺にできるわけねえだろ！
Dialogue: 0,00:07:46.29,00:07:49.14,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,みんな勝手すぎるってばよ。
Dialogue: 0,00:07:49.14,00:07:54.01,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺ってば 頭わりいし\Nそんなにすげえ忍者じゃねえし。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then... It's time for me to go.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:54.01,00:07:56.76,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それに 俺ってば…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My chakra's fading.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:56.76,00:08:00.93,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前なら\Nその答えを見つけられる。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:07:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I will rebuild the seal.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:03.83,00:08:06.75,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺は お前を信じている。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,However, this will be for the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The Leaf can be rebuilt.
