Dialogue: 0,00:10:10.50,00:10:15.19,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,地爆天星から\N這い出てくるとはな。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He is crawling out of\Nthe Planetary Devastation.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:15.19,00:10:17.80,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なんて力だ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What incredible strength.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:17.80,00:10:20.93,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,こうなったら 更に大きな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I must increase the size...
Dialogue: 0,00:10:25.63,00:10:29.59,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,九尾が… 消えた。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The Nine-Tails... disappeared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,His doubt is gone...
Dialogue: 0,00:10:43.20,00:10:48.07,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,迷いが消えたか… 何があった？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he now have control\Nover the Nine-Tails?
Dialogue: 0,00:10:48.07,00:10:53.57,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,すでに九尾を制することが\Nできるというのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagato!
Dialogue: 0,00:10:56.60,00:10:58.65,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(小南)長門！
Dialogue: 0,00:11:25.86,00:11:29.86,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《九尾化したせいで\Nチャクラが乱れちまった。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The transformation into the Nine-Tails\Ndisturbed my chakra.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:11:29.86,00:11:33.89,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,仙術チャクラをストックしてた影分身も\N消えちまってる。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It made me lose my Shadow Clone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:11:33.89,00:11:36.82,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,使える仙術チャクラは➡
Dialogue: 0,00:11:36.82,00:11:39.98,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺自身に\N残ってる分だけってことか》
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can only use the Sage Jutsu Chakra\NI have left inside of me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:12:01.14,00:12:06.84,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《すでに 仙人モードに入ったか…\Nタフなやつだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's already in Sage Mode.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's tough.{\i0}
