Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to confirm the extent\Nof the Nine-Tails' power,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:12:11.37,00:12:14.85,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,まさか 地爆天星まで…》
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I never imagined he could stop\Nmy Planetary Devastation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:12:14.85,00:12:19.72,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(カツユ)プハーッ！\N死ぬかと思いましたよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was going to die!
Dialogue: 0,00:12:19.72,00:12:21.80,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,これって…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,00:12:23.75,00:12:27.92,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あっちは里のほう… あれは？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where the village is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it, Naruto, when you\Nwere in the Nine-Tails state.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:30.15,00:12:33.70,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(カツユ)九尾化した\Nナルト君がやりました。
Dialogue: 0,00:12:37.63,00:12:42.64,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《もしかして\Nヒナタや木ノ葉の人たちを 俺が…》
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I killed Hinata, and the people\Nof the Leaf Village?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She's alive...
Dialogue: 0,00:12:44.70,00:12:49.74,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,生きてる！\Nまだ ヒナタのチャクラが感じられる！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can sense Hinata's chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worried,
Dialogue: 0,00:12:49.74,00:12:54.79,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,心配しました。\Nでも九尾化したナルト君の攻撃で➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but no casualties resulted from\Nyour assault
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Nine-Tails state.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:54.79,00:12:57.95,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,木ノ葉の人々に\N被害は出ていません。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We were lucky.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:57.95,00:13:00.18,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,運よくですが…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:00.18,00:13:07.58,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うん。 そうか… よかった。\Nよかったってばよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness. What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:07.58,00:13:11.90,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《ヒナタ : ナルト君…》
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naruto-kun...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:13:11.90,00:13:14.50,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ネジ)ヒナタ様！
Dialogue: 0,00:13:14.50,00:13:20.25,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(テンテン)致命傷は避けている。\Nでも すぐに治療しないと！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinata-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Her injuries aren't fatal,\Nbut she needs treatment immediately!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:20.25,00:13:23.69,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,今 医療忍者を捜している！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find some Medical Ninja right away.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:27.20,00:13:31.24,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((木ノ葉が暁に襲われた！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Leaf Village is under attack\Nby the Akatsuki!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:13:31.24,00:13:35.90,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(わしゃ もう動けん。\Nはよう行ってくれ))
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I cannot move anymore!\NHurry and go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:13:35.90,00:13:38.72,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ガイ)ここまでとは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know things were this bad.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:40.98,00:13:45.64,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(リー)こちらにも 怪我蛙です。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an injured toad here too.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:57.40,00:14:00.32,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そろそろ決着をつけよう。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to settle this.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:10.28,00:14:13.06,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,少しは 痛みを理解できたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you come to understand\Na little of what pain is?
Dialogue: 0,00:14:13.06,00:14:18.63,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,同じ痛みを知らなければ\N他人を本当には理解できない。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you know the same pain,\Nyou cannot truly know another.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:18.63,00:14:23.53,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そして 理解をしたところで\Nわかり合えるわけでもない。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if you get to know others,\Nthere can be no understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:25.58,00:14:29.41,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それが 道理だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like how it's useless\Nto chase after Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:29.41,00:14:33.06,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前が サスケを追いかけても\N無駄なようにな。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me to where the real you is!
Dialogue: 0,00:14:38.28,00:14:42.98,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前の本体のところへ\N俺を連れていけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to speak to you face-to-face.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:42.98,00:14:46.52,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,直接 話したいことがある。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me to where the real you is!
Dialogue: 0,00:14:51.68,00:14:55.16,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前の本体のところへ\N俺を連れていけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to speak to you face-to-face.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:55.16,00:14:58.08,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,直接 話したいことがある。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... So you figured that out?
Dialogue: 0,00:15:01.28,00:15:05.94,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ほう… 本体に気づいたか。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiraiya-sensei and now you...
Dialogue: 0,00:15:05.94,00:15:11.34,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,自来也先生も お前たちも\N木ノ葉は なかなかやるものだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You Leaf people are quite impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,However, our discussion is over.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:11.34,00:15:14.81,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だが 話は終わった。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Talking with you will change nothing.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:14.81,00:15:18.85,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,今更 お前が何を語っても\N何も変わらん。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me talk to him!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:18.85,00:15:21.60,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,とにかく 話をさせろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sage Mode...
Dialogue: 0,00:15:21.60,00:15:24.63,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,仙人モード…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you can only throw two\Nof those nasty chakra shuriken.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:24.63,00:15:27.62,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あのやっかいな チャクラの手裏剣は➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that so?
Dialogue: 0,00:15:27.62,00:15:31.27,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,２発までしか\N撃つことはできないようだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,After that,\Nyou will run out of Sage Mode!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:31.27,00:15:35.79,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,しかも それで仙人モードは消える。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I have no choice\Nbut to fight you!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:35.79,00:15:38.96,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,やっぱ 戦うしかねえみてえだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If both of your shuriken miss,\Nyou shall lose.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:38.96,00:15:44.49,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もし その２発の手裏剣を外したら\Nお前の負けだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I will give you no more chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left is to dodge your attack, and\Nthen bring your half-dead body with me.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:44.49,00:15:46.61,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もう スキは与えない。
Dialogue: 0,00:15:46.61,00:15:51.55,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,外したら最後\N半殺しにして連れていくだけだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just look for the real Pain myself!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:51.55,00:15:57.36,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なら しかたねえ！\N本体は自分で捜す！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:57.36,00:16:00.39,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,でも どうやって？\N考えがある。
Dialogue: 0,00:16:31.48,00:16:36.14,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《こいつ\N仙人モードで逆探知を…》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He reverse-tracked me using Sage Mode!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:16:36.14,00:16:38.23,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,見つけたぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Found you!
Dialogue: 0,00:16:42.75,00:16:44.84,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,貴様…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,00:16:47.80,00:16:50.72,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,影分身の術！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,00:16:54.58,00:16:56.60,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,よし 煙玉だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Smoke Bombs!
Dialogue: 0,00:16:56.60,00:16:59.00,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,おぉ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:01.75,00:17:04.15,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《まずは １発目…》
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here comes the first shuriken.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Almighty Push!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:07.45,00:17:10.24,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,神羅天征！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?! He had already launched\Nthe second one using Shadow Shuriken Jutsu?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:17:10.24,00:17:14.27,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《なに!? ２発目を\N影手裏剣で放っていただと!?》
Dialogue: 0,00:17:14.27,00:17:18.44,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《インターバルは ５秒…\Nこれならいける！》
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His jutsu interval is five seconds!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can do this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Four seconds to go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:17:38.63,00:17:41.51,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《残り４秒…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was already standing by\Nwith a Shadow Clone back then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:17:41.51,00:17:47.12,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あの時すでに 影分身を\N仕込んでいたとはな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Three more seconds\Nuntil I can use my next jutsu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:17:47.12,00:17:57.21,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,次の術発動まで ３秒…\Nだが ２発外したな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But he missed both shots...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have two more seconds! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He had this many Shadow Clones\Ntransformed into rubble?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One more second!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zero!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He's now using Shadow Clones\Nas back up!
Dialogue: 0,00:18:48.81,00:18:50.90,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,終わりだ！》
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone like you who has no answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,should just give up!
Dialogue: 0,00:18:54.94,00:18:57.02,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なに!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I have faith that{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:18:57.02,00:18:59.60,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,まだ ２秒ある！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there will come a time when\Npeople can truly understand one another.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:18:59.60,00:19:01.68,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いっけ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And if I can't find the answer,\Nperhaps I will entrust you to find it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:19:04.68,00:19:09.16,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《これほどの影分身を\Nがれきに変化させて！》
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know you'll find the answer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have faith in you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:19:13.17,00:19:15.25,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《あと１秒！》
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only you can surpass\Nthe Fourth Hokage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:19:20.26,00:19:22.66,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ゼロ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I truly believe that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:19:28.30,00:19:30.39,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He withstood it... Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,00:19:41.28,00:19:43.36,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,奥から 影分身を…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That jutsu cannot be thrown.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have five seconds.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This distance will work for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:19:45.80,00:19:49.84,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,答えを持たぬ お前ごときが\Nあきらめろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up...
Dialogue: 0,00:19:49.84,00:19:52.41,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うぅっ！ うぅ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...on me giving up!
