Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.86,0:21:40.82,NEP,,0,0,0,,You're here.
Dialogue: 0,00:21:39.02,00:21:42.92,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,人が本当の意味で\N理解し合える時代が来ると➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:43.28,NEP,,0,0,0,,That must mean you defeated the sixth Pain.
