Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.36,0:21:46.57,NEP,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter who won or lost.
Dialogue: 0,00:21:44.94,00:21:46.96,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,答えが見つからんかったときは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.86,0:21:48.28,NEP,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,00:21:46.96,00:21:50.57,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(その答えを\Nお前に託すとしようかのう))
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:52.41,NEP,,0,0,0,,In any case, I'm on my way to see the real Pain.
Dialogue: 0,00:21:50.57,00:21:54.05,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((お前なら\Nその答えを見つけられる。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:54.00,NEP,,0,0,0,,Please don't follow.
Dialogue: 0,00:21:54.05,00:21:56.07,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(俺は お前を信じている))
