Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamato's Room has been\Nrenamed Guy's Room!
Dialogue: 0,00:22:11.03,00:22:13.85,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,耐えた… だと!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, this is your idol...\NMight Guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.31,0:22:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Our guest today is the pride of\Nthe Leaf Village,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,kunoichi Hyuga Hinata!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.73,0:22:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.28,0:22:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw come on.\NDon't be so bashful on my program.
Dialogue: 0,00:22:24.15,00:22:31.21,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《あの術は 投げ飛ばせない…\N５秒… この距離ならいける》
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.03,0:22:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She is extremely introverted and shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.66,0:22:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Her hobby is pressed flower art.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She loves cinnamon rolls and\Nsweet bean jam?
Dialogue: 0,00:22:31.21,00:22:34.65,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺が あきらめるのを…。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget the script!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.83,0:22:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just ask you things\NI'm curious about.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.16,0:22:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what a live,\Nyouthful interview is about!
Dialogue: 0,00:22:38.38,00:22:40.60,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あきらめろ！
Dialogue: 0,00:22:40.60,00:22:42.69,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,螺旋丸！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.75,0:22:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Hinata...
Dialogue: 0,00:22:42.69,00:22:46.41,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(スティング)帰ってきたんだって。\N(ローグ)何の話だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You've really matured lately.\NLet me guess, you're in love, right?
Dialogue: 0,00:22:46.41,00:22:51.28,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(スティング)７年前に失踪した\Nフェアリーテイルの主要メンバー。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.63,0:22:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- W-Well...\N- All right, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Look straight into that camera\Nand say what's in your heart!
Dialogue: 0,00:22:51.28,00:22:55.28,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ローグ)興味ないな。\Nウソをつくなよ ローグ。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.43,0:22:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.60,0:22:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're too shy, I'll help you!
Dialogue: 0,00:22:55.28,00:22:58.40,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あれほど憧れたナツさんだぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.56,0:22:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:22:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.98,0:22:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, love confession in...
Dialogue: 0,00:22:58.40,00:23:01.53,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ローグ)昔の話だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.35,0:23:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,three, two, one, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.23,0:23:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can't!
